Suggests: wl-clipboard, xclip
Description: CLI tool for creating beautiful code screenshots
 Goshot is a powerful CLI tool and library for creating beautiful code
 screenshots with customizable features. It offers syntax highlighting
 with multiple themes, customizable window chrome styles, various
 background options including gradients and images, and supports
 multiple export formats.
 .
 Perfect for developers looking to create stunning visual representations
 of their code for documentation, presentations, or social media sharing.
